name: generate_signature
description:
This is a sub-function API for tool tiktok_v2.
Tool description: Highly maintain and accurate T-tok API to  fetch profiles or feeds in bulk. 
API description: Generate Signature from TikToc API Url

Following API Path will work with this signature

/node/share/user/
/api/post/itemlist/
/api/challenge/itemlist/
/api/music/item_list/

url.description: The TikTok API URL for which to generate the signature.
